Pursuit force reporting.

517
00:47:38,375 --> 00:47:41,712
我们失去了逃跑目标的可视联系 等待下一步命令
We lost visual contact with escaped units. Awaiting further orders.

518
00:47:41,712 --> 00:47:45,341
