520
00:47:48,761 --> 00:47:50,929
我们最好这样 无用的家伙
We'd better, null unit.

521
00:47:50,929 --> 00:47:55,351
我会感到非常幸运 如果主控制程序不杀了我
I will be lucky if the MCP doesn't blast me into a dead zone.

522
00:47:55,351 --> 00:47:57,269
我要抓住他们！
I want those conscripts.

523
00:48:05,944 --> 00:48:08,864
那是什么？你看见了什么？
What is it? What do you see?

524
00:48:08,864 --> 00:48:10,908
当心
Watch it. Watch it.

525
00:48:15,996 --> 00:48:17,915
来吧 你这个小家伙
Come on, you little bugger.

526
00:48:17,915 --> 00:48:20,376
看
Look at that.

527
00:48:20,376 --> 00:48:24,755
我们什么时候可以拜访主控制程序？
When do we pay our visit to the old Master Control?

528
00:48:24,755 --> 00:48:26,799
什么？
What?

529
00:48:27,966 --> 00:48:31,220
我们只有三个人
There's just three of us.

530
00:48:31,220 --> 00:48:34,056
如果你认识什么雇佣军 很好
Well, if you know anybody who's got an army for rent, that's fine,

531
00:48:34,056 --> 00:48:37,559
但我的用户要我揪出那个家伙
but my User told me to go take that sucker out,

532
00:48:37,559 --> 00:48:39,561
否则我就会不去了
or I am never getting out of here.

533
00:48:39,561 --> 00:48:41,772
我们不可能找到主控制程序…
We can't get to the MCP...

534
00:48:41,772 --> 00:48:43,857
除非有我的用户的帮助
without the help of my User.

535
00:48:45,984 --> 00:48:48,278
我必须到那个输入/输出塔
I have to get to that input/output tower,

536
00:48:48,278 --> 00:48:50,322
和他联络
and communicate with him.

537
00:48:53,242 --> 00:48:56,078
向艾伦报到 也许他知道…
Well, good. Check in with Alan. Maybe he knows what's...

538
00:48:56,078 --> 00:48:58,247
那是什么？
What's that?

539
00:48:58,247 --> 00:49:01,166
那… 只是…
That... is just...

540
00:49:01,166 --> 00:49:04,128
我现在就想要的
what I need right now.

541
00:49:20,269 --> 00:49:22,354
太棒了
Oh, it's nice.

542
00:49:29,361 --> 00:49:32,322
难以置信
Incredible.

543
00:49:41,373 --> 00:49:44,459
孩子 你已经忘记了能量的美好感觉…
Boy, you forget how good the power feels...

544
00:49:44,459 --> 00:49:46,461
除非你找到一个纯能量源
until you get to a pure source.

545
00:49:49,381 --> 00:49:52,384
我的朋友们 我的同盟军
My friends, my fellow conscripts, we have scored.

546
00:49:52,384 --> 00:49:55,012
我们已经恢复了！我感觉好多了
I feel so much better.

547
00:49:59,224 --> 00:50:01,810
