Moving into next sector.

549
00:50:09,902 --> 00:50:11,820
- 谢谢 - 我能感觉到他
- Thank you. - I can feel it.

550
00:50:11,820 --> 00:50:15,699
感觉到什么？你还好吧？
Feel what? You okay?

551
00:50:18,076 --> 00:50:19,995
艾伦-1
Alan-1.

552
00:50:21,580 --> 00:50:23,540
出发！
Let's move out.

553
00:50:34,301 --> 00:50:36,219
来吧 弗林 别喝了
Come on, Flynn, put a cork in it.

554
00:50:36,219 --> 00:50:39,181
一秒钟！
One second.

555
00:51:09,795 --> 00:51:11,838
射程… 9
Range, 9.

556
00:51:11,838 --> 00:51:15,092
位置… 45 48 度
Mark, 45. 48 degrees.

557
00:51:21,056 --> 00:51:22,557
稳住
Hold it.

558
00:51:22,557 --> 00:51:24,935
稳住 开火！
Hold it. Fire.

559
00:51:37,322 --> 00:51:39,074
拉姆 弗林 听见了吗？
Ram, Flynn, do you read me?

560
00:51:39,074 --> 00:51:41,785
追击部队报告 2个逃跑单位被消灭
Pursuit force reporting. Two escaped units de-rezzed.

561
00:51:41,785 --> 00:51:42,535
不
No.

562
00:51:55,715 --> 00:51:57,801
创逃入下一个扇区
Tron unit heading into next sector.

563
00:52:04,141 --> 00:52:05,141
拉姆？
Ram?

564
00:52:06,643 --> 00:52:07,643
拉姆
Ram.

565
00:52:09,855 --> 00:52:13,859
快点 我们要离开这里
Come on. We got to get out of here.

566
00:52:16,903 --> 00:52:18,864
没有生命迹象 看上去我们消灭他们了
No sign of life. Looks like we got them.

567
00:52:28,039 --> 00:52:30,625
继续追击逃跑的新兵
Continue pursuit of remaining conscript.

568
00:52:30,625 --> 00:52:33,712
明白 向扇区边界前进
Acknowledged. Proceeding towards sector frontier.

569
00:52:37,716 --> 00:52:39,634
我们能做到的 拉姆
We're going to make it, Ram.

570
00:52:39,634 --> 00:52:42,220
我们要替你找个地方休息一下
I just got to find you a place to rest.

571
00:52:57,569 --> 00:53:00,864
在那里停一下 拉姆 看上去不错的地方
Hang in there, Ram. This looks like a good spot.

572
00:53:10,248 --> 00:53:12,792
那些坦克不会到这里来找我们的
Those tanks won't find us here.

573
00:53:14,085 --> 00:53:16,087
好吧
Okay.

574
00:53:19,090 --> 00:53:21,217
我以为这会很简单的
I thought this was supposed to be easy.

575
00:53:54,960 --> 00:53:57,587
发生了什么？
Hey, what's going on?

576
00:54:03,301 --> 00:54:05,387
你看见了吗？
You see this?

577
00:54:05,387 --> 00:54:08,139
你怎么做到的？
You shouldn't be able to do that.

578
00:54:17,732 --> 00:54:20,193
现在来些真正用户的力量
Now for some real User power.

579
00:54:51,141 --> 00:54:53,977
这个看上去还能用
Hey, this looks promising.

580
00:54:59,149 --> 00:55:02,193
这个看上去向老式控制器
This is just like the old arcade grips.

581
00:55:05,321 --> 00:55:08,491
让我们上路吧
Let's get this show on the road.

582
00:55:17,208 --> 00:55:19,419
现在我们启动了
Now we're smoking.

583
00:55:19,419 --> 00:55:21,671
你怎么能偷一个守卫者？
How can you steal a Recognizer?

584
00:55:21,671 --> 00:55:23,882
你没事吧？你看上去不太好
Hey, you okay? You don't look so good.

585
00:55:23,882 --> 00:55:27,218
- 我们要想办法让你好起来 - 过来
- We will get you fixed up. Hang on. - Come here.

586
00:55:50,992 --> 00:55:53,828
我的用户！
Oh, my User.

587
00:55:53,828 --> 00:55:56,331
用户 用户 他们…
Users are Users. They...

588
00:56:00,752 --> 00:56:02,712
你是一个用户？
Are you a User?

589
00:56:16,684 --> 00:56:17,404
弗林
Flynn,

590
00:56:19,938 --> 00:56:21,856
帮助创
help Tron.

591
00:56:32,450 --> 00:56:33,450
拉姆
Ram.

592
00:56:42,794 --> 00:56:43,794
拉姆
Ram.

593
00:57:29,632 --> 00:57:31,634
该死的守卫者
Damn Recognizer.

594
00:57:34,220 --> 00:57:36,264
只要直行
Thing just goes straight.

595
00:57:36,264 --> 00:57:39,934
我要到那个I/O塔
I got to get to that l/O tower.

596
00:57:39,934 --> 00:57:44,856
程序Alu 要求2号扇区的补充信息
Program Alu, request additional information for sector two.

597
00:57:44,856 --> 00:57:47,900
准备游戏模拟输送
Prepare hangar for game simulation transport.

598
00:57:47,900 --> 00:57:51,779
所有单位注意 抓紧矩阵代码
Attention all units, lock onto matrix code.

599
00:57:51,779 --> 00:57:53,906
准备数字光束传输
Prepare for digital beam transport.

600
00:57:53,906 --> 00:57:55,992
启动门
Activate hangar doors.

601
00:57:59,328 --> 00:58:01,748
模拟的进展如何？
What's the progress on the simulation?

602
00:58:01,748 --> 00:58:05,418
30 56 99正确
30, 56, 99 are correct.

603
00:58:05,418 --> 00:58:08,963
限制4 和 8失败
Limited four and eight are missing.

604
00:58:13,760 --> 00:58:17,263
别叫 尤里
Don't scream. Yori.

605
00:58:17,263 --> 00:58:19,932
30 56 99正确
30, 56, 99 are correct.

606
00:58:19,932 --> 00:58:22,435
受限的4和8不见了
Limited four and eight are missing.

607
00:58:22,435 --> 00:58:24,437
不 我…
No, I...

608
00:58:27,231 --> 00:58:29,150
创！
Tron.

609
00:58:31,819 --> 00:58:33,069
尤里
Yori.

610
00:58:35,448 --> 00:58:38,451
我知道你已经逃跑了
I knew you'd escape.

611
00:58:38,451 --> 00:58:41,078
他们还没有造出一个可以抓住你的电路来
They haven't built a circuit that could hold you.

612
00:58:41,078 --> 00:58:44,457
听着！我们必须要制定一个计划
Listen. We have to make plans.

613
00:58:44,457 --> 00:58:46,959
我们可以到哪里去？
Where can we go?

614
00:58:51,672 --> 00:58:54,258
这边 快
This way, quickly.

615
00:59:06,062 --> 00:59:08,564
停在那里！
Hold it right there.

616
00:59:08,564 --> 00:59:10,650
- 是？ - 什么意思“是”？
- Yes? - What do you mean, "yes"?

617
00:59:10,650 --> 00:59:11,650
是
Yes.

618
00:59:12,735 --> 00:59:15,780
你只会说那个吗？
Is that all you can say?

619
00:59:16,906 --> 00:59:17,656
不
No.

620
00:59:18,908 --> 00:59:21,661
- 别的什么？ - 是
- Anything else? - Yes.

621
00:59:23,704 --> 00:59:25,998
正和反 嗯？你是一个位
Positive and negative, huh? You're a bit.

622
00:59:25,998 --> 00:59:26,998
是
Yes.

623
00:59:28,918 --> 00:59:31,587
你的程序在哪里？他把你丢了？
Where's your program? Isn't he going to miss you?

624
00:59:31,587 --> 00:59:35,341
- 不 - 我是你的程序
- No. - I am your program.

625
00:59:35,341 --> 00:59:39,262
- 是 - 又多一张嘴要喂了
- Yes. - Another mouth to feed.

626
00:59:39,262 --> 00:59:42,890
是-是-是-是！
Yes-yes-yes-yes-yes.

627
00:59:51,107 --> 00:59:54,026
注意嵌套宏
Watch out for nested macros.

628
00:59:55,945 --> 00:59:58,698
- 那些古怪的人是谁？ - 无用的数据
- Who are these weirdos? - Inoperative data pushers.

629
00:59:58,698 --> 01:00:01,450
控制程序！来吧
Control programs. Come on.

630
01:00:02,868 --> 01:00:05,371
高超的驾驶技术 嗯？
Pretty good driving, huh? Oh.

631
01:00:09,083 --> 01:00:13,004
- 不！ - 谁问你了？
- No. - Who asked you?

632
01:00:27,309 --> 01:00:30,062
不-不-不-不！
No-no-no-no.

633
01:00:47,997 --> 01:00:51,917
这家伙在城里不太好控制
This baby doesn't handle so good in town. No.

634
01:00:55,671 --> 01:00:58,424
- 这是干什么的？ 这个呢？ - 不 不
- What's this do? How about this one? - No. No.

635
01:01:00,676 --> 01:01:03,429
头疼
Here comes a headache.

636
01:01:05,347 --> 01:01:07,892
- 啊 - 不-不-不-不！
- Aah. - No-no-no-no.

637
01:01:10,519 --> 01:01:13,522
- 我们要停下这家伙 - 是
- We got to stop this thing. - Yes.

638
01:01:13,522 --> 01:01:17,026
很高兴你同意！
I am glad you agree.

639
01:01:38,714 --> 01:01:41,675
我很好 没问题
Uh, I am fine. No problem.

640
01:01:44,762 --> 01:01:47,932
这个镇上有很多人
Oh, this town is full of live ones.

641
01:02:00,319 --> 01:02:02,696
这就是创说要去的地方
This is where Tron said he was going.

642
01:02:05,741 --> 01:02:07,952
失败的弗林
Losing Flynn.

643
01:02:37,815 --> 01:02:39,984
我不能相信这个
I don't believe this.

644
01:02:51,745 --> 01:02:53,330
站住！
Halt.

645
01:03:00,879 --> 01:03:02,798
更多守卫
More guards.

646
01:03:58,645 --> 01:04:01,732
他们没有看见我们 我走前面
They don't see us. I will go first.

647
01:04:24,379 --> 01:04:26,298
你还好吗？
Are you all right?

648
01:04:26,298 --> 01:04:28,675
是的 让我们再来一遍
Yeah. Let's do that some more.

649
01:04:28,675 --> 01:04:30,803
我想那个警卫看见我了
I think the guard saw me.

650
01:04:30,803 --> 01:04:32,846
来吧！
Come on.

651
01:04:39,561 --> 01:04:42,898
- 站住 - 杜蒙特
- Halt. - Dumont.

652
01:04:42,898 --> 01:04:45,484
我不能支持暴动 你想要什么？
I can't stand this commotion. What do you want?

653
01:04:45,484 --> 01:04:47,903
我来和我的用户联络
I have come to communicate with my User.

654
01:04:47,903 --> 01:04:52,533
困难的提议… 最困难的提议
Difficult proposition. Difficult proposition at best.

655
01:04:52,533 --> 01:04:55,661
让你们进去会令我被毁灭的
Why, I could be de-rezzed just for letting you in here.

656
01:04:55,661 --> 01:05:01,166
他们讨厌这个塔 他们不是不敢关闭它
They hate this tower. They'd close it down if they dared.

657
01:05:01,166 --> 01:05:03,252
他们留着我只是为了…
They keep me around just in case one of them...

658
01:05:03,252 --> 01:05:05,921
万一要和别的世界联络
wants to deal with the other world once in a while.

659
01:05:05,921 --> 01:05:06,761
杜蒙特
Dumont.

660
01:05:09,091 --> 01:05:13,178
我的用户说…
My User has information that could...

661
01:05:13,178 --> 01:05:15,597
可以让这里恢复成自由系统
could make this a free system again.

662
01:05:15,597 --> 01:05:17,349
不 是真的！
No, really.

663
01:05:17,349 --> 01:05:21,186
你应该有程序连线来使用这个地方
You'd have programs lined up to use this place,

664
01:05:21,186 --> 01:05:24,022
并且没有主控制程序监视
and no MCP looking over your shoulder.

665
01:05:24,022 --> 01:05:26,316
当你和我在这个系统中呆上一样长的时间
When you have been in the system as long as I have,

666
01:05:26,316 --> 01:05:28,652
你会听到很多承诺 安慰
you hear many promises, many reassurances,

667
01:05:28,652 --> 01:05:31,697
- 很多勇敢的计划 - 求求你？
- many brave plans. - Please, Dumont.

668
01:05:33,115 --> 01:05:36,368
警卫们来了
The guards are coming.

669
01:05:36,368 --> 01:05:38,495
他们和守卫者在一起
There they are with the guardian.

670
01:05:38,495 --> 01:05:41,081
好吧 尤里
All right, Yori. All right.

671
01:05:43,458 --> 01:05:46,044
谁是你的用户 程序？
Who is your User, program?

672
01:05:47,796 --> 01:05:49,715
艾伦-1
Alan-1.

673
01:05:49,715 --> 01:05:52,050
他调用我 我可以过去吗？
He calls me. May I pass?

674
01:05:52,050 --> 01:05:55,220
所有可见的…
All that is visible...

675
01:05:55,220 --> 01:05:57,556
都必须超越自己
must grow beyond itself,

676
01:05:57,556 --> 01:06:00,392
到达不可见的领域
and extend into the realm of the invisible.

677
01:06:00,392 --> 01:06:03,478
你可以过去 我的朋友
You may pass, my friend.

678
01:06:12,904 --> 01:06:15,490
塔守卫者在帮他
The tower guardian is helping him.

679
01:06:15,490 --> 01:06:17,659
他想
He thinks.

680
01:06:17,659 --> 01:06:19,995
把逻辑探针拿来
Bring in the logic probe.

681
01:06:37,637 --> 01:06:40,807
加大能量！
More power.

682
01:07:41,159 --> 01:07:43,078
开始了
It's begun.

683
01:07:44,538 --> 01:07:47,123
创 定位询问 确定
Tron, location query. Confirm.

684
01:07:47,123 --> 01:07:49,459
确定 艾伦-1
Confirmed, Alan-1.

685
01:07:49,459 --> 01:07:51,670
我正在你的碟片里生成信息…
I am creating the information on your disk...

686
01:07:51,670 --> 01:07:55,465
那将会清除主控制程序并改变系统
that will erase the MCP and change the system.

687
01:07:55,465 --> 01:07:59,594
你尽力将这个碟片送入主控制程序的心脏
Dedicate yourself to getting the disk into the heart...of the MCP.

688
01:07:59,594 --> 01:08:02,138
