691
01:08:18,321 --> 01:08:21,533
这是通往新秩序的钥匙
This is the key to a new order.

692
01:08:21,533 --> 01:08:25,579
这个代码碟意味着自由
This code disk means freedom.

693
01:08:26,955 --> 01:08:29,833
我想他们要闯进来了
I think they're breaking in.

694
01:08:37,549 --> 01:08:40,719
- 谢谢 杜蒙特 - 快点 用户们在等着
- Thank you, Dumont. - Hurry. The Users are waiting.

695
01:08:56,109 --> 01:08:57,861
杜蒙特？
Dumont?

696
01:09:01,281 --> 01:09:04,075
程序在哪里？
Where's the program?

697
01:09:04,075 --> 01:09:06,244
什么程序？
What program?

698
01:09:07,662 --> 01:09:09,623
抓住它！
Take him.

699
01:09:19,090 --> 01:09:21,426
靠近点
Stay close.

700
01:09:30,935 --> 01:09:34,981
如果我能让我们到达扫描输送光束
If I can just get us on the scanning transport beam,

701
01:09:34,981 --> 01:09:38,777
模拟会通过游戏区把我们…
this solar sail simulation will take us across the game sea,

702
01:09:38,777 --> 01:09:41,029
送入中央电脑
out of this domain, back into the central computer.

703
01:09:49,371 --> 01:09:51,289
当心！
Look out.

704
01:11:11,452 --> 01:11:16,207
指挥官 你已经享受到了你所赋予的力量
Commander, you have enjoyed all the power you have been given, haven't you?

705
01:11:16,207 --> 01:11:20,169
我很想知道你在一个计算器里会是什么样子
I wonder how you'd take to working in a pocket calculator.

706
01:11:20,169 --> 01:11:22,589
我们搞定了那个你送来的用户
We did take care of that User you sent us.

707
01:11:22,589 --> 01:11:25,884
无效零 现在你有两个叛逃程序…
Incompetent zero, now you have got two renegade programs...

708
01:11:25,884 --> 01:11:28,553
通过被窃的模拟在系统中到处串
flying all over the system in a stolen simulation.

709
01:11:28,553 --> 01:11:32,515
我会抓住他们的 这只是时间问题
We will get them. It's only a matter of time.

710
01:11:32,515 --> 01:11:35,226
你就要到最后关头了
You have almost reached your decision gate,

711
01:11:35,226 --> 01:11:37,478
我不会给你更多的时间了
and I can't spare you any more time.

712
01:11:37,478 --> 01:11:39,480
结束
End of line.

713
01:11:46,905 --> 01:11:49,365
- 是我 弗林 - 弗林
- It's me... Flynn. - Flynn.

714
01:11:49,365 --> 01:11:52,368
- 恭喜 程序 - 你还活着
- Greetings, program. - You're alive.

715
01:11:53,328 --> 01:11:57,373
勉强 是的 我 呃…
Barely. Yeah, I, uh...

716
01:12:12,347 --> 01:12:14,265
拉姆在哪里？
Where's Ram?

717
01:12:14,265 --> 01:12:16,643
他没挺过来
He didn't make it.

718
01:12:25,610 --> 01:12:27,528
来吧
Come on.

719
01:12:40,541 --> 01:12:41,791
罗拉
Lora.

720
01:12:43,544 --> 01:12:46,631
这是弗林 救我出来的
This is Flynn. The one who busted me out.

721
01:12:46,631 --> 01:12:48,132
罗拉？
Lora?

722
01:12:48,132 --> 01:12:50,760
好的 我该谢谢他
Well, then I owe him some thanks.

723
01:12:52,970 --> 01:12:55,848
那没什么
No, it's, uh, no big deal.

724
01:12:55,848 --> 01:12:58,976
我应该了解轻型赛车 我写了那个程序
I ought to know my way around the Lightcycle. I wrote the program.

725
01:12:58,976 --> 01:13:02,146
- 你写了那个程序？ - 我该对你说实话了
- You wrote the program? - It's time I level with you.

726
01:13:02,146 --> 01:13:06,484
- 我是一个用户 - 你是一个用户？
- I am what you guys call a User. - You're a User?

727
01:13:06,484 --> 01:13:08,611
我在什么地方走错路了
I took a wrong turn somewhere.

728
01:13:08,611 --> 01:13:11,280
如果你是一个用户
If you are a User,

729
01:13:11,280 --> 01:13:13,491
你所做的每一件事都是有计划的 对吗
everything you have done has been according to a plan, right?

730
01:13:13,491 --> 01:13:15,743
想的美
You wish.

731
01:13:15,743 --> 01:13:18,788
你知道那象什么
You guys know what it's like.

732
01:13:18,788 --> 01:13:22,166
你只是做你应该做的 无论那有多疯狂
You keep doing what it looks like you're supposed to, no matter how crazy it seems.

733
01:13:22,166 --> 01:13:25,002
程序就是这样的 是的
That's the way it is for programs, yes.

734
01:13:25,002 --> 01:13:29,006
不愿让你失望 朋友 但多数时候用户也是这样的
Hate to disappoint you, pal, but most of the time, that's the way it is for Users too.

735
01:13:29,006 --> 01:13:31,634
奇怪 奇怪
Stranger and stranger.

736
01:13:31,634 --> 01:13:35,263
哦 你们的船很好看
So, nice-looking ship you got here.

737
01:13:54,949 --> 01:13:57,577
你想怎么处理那个塔守卫者 杜蒙特？
What do you want done with the tower guardian... Dumont?

738
01:13:57,577 --> 01:13:59,954
和其他人关在一起？
Put him with the others?

739
01:13:59,954 --> 01:14:02,707
不 笨蛋 准备提审
No, bit brain, prepare him for inquisition.

740
01:14:02,707 --> 01:14:04,709
我需要点娱乐
I need a little bit of relaxation.

741
01:14:04,709 --> 01:14:06,752
首先 准备好追击战舰
First, rezz up the carrier for pursuit.

742
01:14:06,752 --> 01:14:10,006
还有 不要再思考
One other thing. Don't think any more.

743
01:14:10,006 --> 01:14:12,300
这里我来思考
I do the thinking around here.

744
01:14:18,055 --> 01:14:19,974
这不容易
This isn't going to be easy.

745
01:14:19,974 --> 01:14:22,560
如果那些虫子抓到我们 我们就完了
If those grid bugs get us, we have had it.

746
01:14:46,167 --> 01:14:48,085
够了吗？
Had enough?

747
01:14:48,085 --> 01:14:50,421
你要什么？我很忙
What do you want? I am busy.

748
01:14:50,421 --> 01:14:53,925
忙着死 你这个不可饶恕的老程序
Busy dying, you worn out excuse for an old program.

749
01:14:53,925 --> 01:14:56,302
是的 我很老
Yes, I am old.

750
01:14:56,302 --> 01:15:00,097
老得足够能记起来主控制程序只是一个象棋程序
Old enough to remember the MCP when it was a chess program.

751
01:15:00,097 --> 01:15:02,767
他从小开始也会到小结束
He started small, and he will end small.

752
01:15:02,767 --> 01:15:06,979
很有趣 也许我应该把你留在身边娱乐
Very funny, Dumont. Maybe I should keep you around just to make me laugh.

753
01:15:17,823 --> 01:15:20,284
- 发生了什么？ - 主控制程序能量脉冲
- What's happening? - Power surge in the MCP.

754
01:15:20,284 --> 01:15:22,745
- 我们得离开这条光束 - 我不能
- We have to get off this beam. - I can't.

755
01:15:22,745 --> 01:15:24,955
在7和8纳秒没有其它的交点
There isn't another junction for seven or eight nanoseconds.

756
01:15:26,123 --> 01:15:28,417
- 那有另一条光束！ - 太远了
- There's another beam. - It's too far.

757
01:15:47,687 --> 01:15:49,313
他在制造一个交点
He's creating a junction.

758
01:16:12,086 --> 01:16:14,171
我们成功了？
Did we make it?

759
01:16:14,171 --> 01:16:16,173
是的
Yeah.

760
01:16:16,173 --> 01:16:18,384
为我方欢呼
Hooray for our side.

761
01:16:42,575 --> 01:16:44,827
他分解了吗？
Is he de-rezzing?

762
01:16:44,827 --> 01:16:48,122
没有 但我不知道为什么
No, but I couldn't tell you why not.

763
01:16:50,875 --> 01:16:53,919
我是一体的
I am all in one piece.

764
01:16:53,919 --> 01:16:56,172
我仍和你们在一起
I guess I am still with you.

765
01:16:58,048 --> 01:17:01,802
叫那个拿手提钻的人停下
Tell the guy with the jackhammer to lay off.

766
01:17:01,802 --> 01:17:04,847
- 你怎么做到的？ - 基本定律:
- How'd you do that? - Elementary physics...

767
01:17:04,847 --> 01:17:06,849
一束能量可以被转向
a beam of energy can always be diverted.

768
01:17:06,849 --> 01:17:09,143
我们到了吗 妈咪？
Are we there yet, Mommy?

769
01:18:03,489 --> 01:18:05,616
萨克！
Sark.

770
01:18:19,630 --> 01:18:22,257
- 杜蒙特！ - 尤里
- Dumont. - Yori.

771
01:18:24,051 --> 01:18:26,053
创？
Tron?

772
01:18:27,721 --> 01:18:30,015
创死了
Tron's dead.

773
01:18:32,476 --> 01:18:35,396
- 那是什么？ - 那是一个用户 杜蒙特
- Who's that? - That is a User, Dumont.

774
01:18:35,396 --> 01:18:38,982
他来帮我们
He came here to help us.

775
01:18:38,982 --> 01:18:42,486
创信任他
Tron believed in him.

776
01:18:43,737 --> 01:18:46,990
如果用户们不再帮我们 我们就输了
If the Users can no longer help us, we're lost.

777
01:18:46,990 --> 01:18:49,827
所以 我们删了那个程序…
So, we have erased that program...

778
01:18:49,827 --> 01:18:50,577
不
No.

779
01:18:51,870 --> 01:18:54,665
- 你被分解了 - 不是我 萨克
- You were de-rezzed. - Not me, Sark.

780
01:18:54,665 --> 01:18:58,001
你没什么了不起的 只是一个二进制程序
There's nothing special about you. You're just an ordinary program.

781
01:18:58,001 --> 01:19:00,796
你也是 应该被删除的一分子
So are you, one that should have been erased.

782
01:19:00,796 --> 01:19:03,507
你什么都不是
You're nothing.

783
01:19:03,507 --> 01:19:06,635
把那个程序送到牢房去
Take that program to the holding pit.

784
01:19:15,185 --> 01:19:17,855
请！不要…
Please, don't take...

785
01:19:17,855 --> 01:19:19,857
我会把我们的朋友…
I am taking our friend here...

786
01:19:19,857 --> 01:19:22,901
和另外那些宗教狂送给主控制程序
and some other religious fanatics to Master Control.

787
01:19:24,570 --> 01:19:26,488
当我登陆后
When I disembark,

788
01:19:26,488 --> 01:19:29,575
仍留在这艘船上的一切…
this ship and everything that remains on board...

789
01:19:29,575 --> 01:19:32,202
都会被自动分解
will automatically de-rezz.

790
01:19:34,705 --> 01:19:37,541
永别了
This means you.

791
01:19:43,297 --> 01:19:45,215
继续前进！
Move on.

792
01:20:13,285 --> 01:20:15,704
直接向量分离
Immediate vectors detached.

793
01:20:15,704 --> 01:20:17,706
送我们去主控制程序
Route us to the MCP.

794
01:20:17,706 --> 01:20:20,167
我想摆脱净负载
I want to get rid of this dead weight,

795
01:20:20,167 --> 01:20:22,836
赶上通向游戏主域的传输光束
and catch a transport beam to the game domain.

796
01:20:31,470 --> 01:20:36,141
这些墙… 尤里 有些事发生了
These walls... Yori, something's happening.

797
01:21:40,372 --> 01:21:43,458
你没事吧？
You all right?

798
01:21:43,458 --> 01:21:46,044
我还有能量 萨克不知道
I still have power. Sark doesn't know that.

799
01:21:47,546 --> 01:21:49,464
让我独自呆着 我们失败了
Leave me alone. We have failed.

800
01:21:49,464 --> 01:21:53,135
只有当我们放弃时！来吧 看 这墙！
We're only going to fail if we give up. Come on, look, the wall.

801
01:21:55,262 --> 01:21:57,139
尤里
Yori.

802
01:22:05,188 --> 01:22:08,150
你把我救回来了
You brought me back.

803
01:22:08,150 --> 01:22:11,445
怎么做的？为什么要把我救回来？
How? Why did you bring me back?

804
01:22:11,445 --> 01:22:13,739
我需要你的帮助 来吧！
I need your help. Come on.

805
01:22:43,560 --> 01:22:45,562
操作控制器！
Do something with these controls.

806
01:22:45,562 --> 01:22:48,106
我在操作
I am on it.

807
01:22:48,106 --> 01:22:50,150
主控制程序 整个系统的心脏
The MCP, it's the heart of the whole system.

808
01:23:14,174 --> 01:23:17,886
我感觉到一个存在 平台上有另一个斗士
I feel a presence. Another warrior is on the mesa.

809
01:23:20,889 --> 01:23:22,807
萨克！
Sark.

810
01:23:25,393 --> 01:23:28,188
我们越来越近
We're getting closer.

811
01:23:31,858 --> 01:23:33,777
我不知道你是怎么幸存下来的
I don't know how you survived.

812
01:23:33,777 --> 01:23:36,988
那无关紧要
Slave, it doesn't matter.

813
01:23:36,988 --> 01:23:40,325
准备受死吧
Prepare to terminate.

814
01:23:52,254 --> 01:23:55,507
所有的程序都是有用的
All programs have a desire to be useful.

815
01:23:55,507 --> 01:23:58,468
很快 你们就不需要寻求相互之间…
But in moments, you will no longer seek communication...

816
01:23:58,468 --> 01:24:02,347
或和用户的通讯了
with each other or your superfluous Users.

817
01:24:02,347 --> 01:24:06,226
你们会成为我的一部分 和我完全在一起
You will each be part of me. Together, we will be complete.

818
01:24:13,608 --> 01:24:16,569
你应该加入我 我们在一起会很强大
You should have joined me. We'd have made a great team.

819
01:24:20,448 --> 01:24:23,827
- 你很顽固 - 我也比你厉害
- You're very persistent. - I am also better than you.

820
01:24:38,258 --> 01:24:39,508
萨克？
Sark?

821
01:24:40,593 --> 01:24:44,472
我所有的功能都给你了
All my functions are now yours. Take them.

822
01:24:46,474 --> 01:24:48,018
萨克？
Sark?

823
01:24:51,813 --> 01:24:53,565
萨克？
Sark?

824
01:24:59,654 --> 01:25:02,157
看！
Look at that.

825
01:25:17,172 --> 01:25:21,009
你的用户再也不能帮你了 我的小程序
Your User can't help you now, my little program.

826
01:25:32,020 --> 01:25:34,397
我有办法了 驶向那条光束
I got it. Steer us over by the beam.

827
01:25:34,397 --> 01:25:36,566
紧靠着它
Right next to it.

828
01:25:36,566 --> 01:25:39,152
那有什么用？
What good will that do?

829
01:25:39,152 --> 01:25:41,196
我要跳下去
I am going to jump.

830
01:25:42,697 --> 01:25:44,949
那是唯一能帮助创的
It's the only way to help Tron.

831
01:25:44,949 --> 01:25:46,993
别 你会被分解的
Don't. You will be de-rezzed.

832
01:26:05,720 --> 01:26:07,722
别担心
Don't worry.

833
01:27:14,956 --> 01:27:18,084
来吧 出发！
Come on, let's go.

834
01:28:00,668 --> 01:28:02,754
我们成功了！
We did it.

835
01:28:11,888 --> 01:28:13,806
太好了
That's nice.

836
01:28:13,806 --> 01:28:16,934
我们以为你死了
We thought you were dead.

837
01:28:16,934 --> 01:28:19,270
- 弗林在哪里？ - 这难以置信
- Where's Flynn? - It was incredible.

838
01:28:19,270 --> 01:28:21,856
他跳进那条光束扰乱主控制程序…
He threw himself into the beam and distracted the MCP...

839
01:28:21,856 --> 01:28:25,026
足以让你把碟片送进去
just long enough for you to get the disk in.

840
01:28:25,026 --> 01:28:27,862
他救了我们 他真的做到了
He saved us. He really did it.

841
01:28:27,862 --> 01:28:30,907
看那些I/O塔
Video warriors, look at the I/O towers.

842
01:28:33,367 --> 01:28:36,245
所有的塔都启动了
Every tower is lighting up.

843
01:29:29,757 --> 01:29:31,884
优先级别一！
Priority one.

844
01:30:28,774 --> 01:30:31,652
尽量看上去专业些 老板来了
Try to look official. Here comes the boss.

845
01:30:48,377 --> 01:30:51,422
一个小时后来接我
Pick me up in an hour. Thanks.

846
01:30:51,422 --> 01:30:54,008
恭喜 程序
Greetings, programs.
